#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/bad_messages_populator.vala:168
#, c-format
msgid ""
"%s has been using an untrusted device. You won't see messages from devices "
"that you do not trust."
msgstr ""
"Chel pandolo di %s al doprave un tramai che no si fidin. No tu iodarâs "
"mesagjos di tramais che no si po fidasi."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/bad_messages_populator.vala:169
msgid "Manage devices"
msgstr "Gjestis i tramais"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/bad_messages_populator.vala:171
#, c-format
msgid ""
"%s does not trust this device. That means, you might be missing messages."
msgstr ""
"Chel pandolo di %s no si fide di te. Cuindi tu podaresis pierditi mesagjos."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:34
msgid "Manage Key"
msgstr "Dai po gjestis las clâs"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:35
msgid ""
"Compare the fingerprint, character by character, with the one shown on your "
"contact's device."
msgstr ""
"Controle las improntes digitâl, ogni latare, cun chês dal contat sul tramai."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:36
msgid "Fingerprints differ"
msgstr "Improntes difarent gnogno"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:37
msgid "Fingerprints match"
msgstr "Brao, las improntes son compagnes"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:38
#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:81
#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:87
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Lasce sta"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:39
msgid "Confirm"
msgstr "Va ben"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:59
msgid "Verify key"
msgstr "Controlant la clâf"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:60
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Future messages sent by %s from the device that uses this key will be "
"highlighted accordingly in the chat window."
msgstr ""
"I mesagjos di chel taconele di %s sal dopre il stes tramai cun chist clâf a "
"saran evidensiâs."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:70
msgid "Fingerprints do not match"
msgstr "Las improntes no son compagnes totoloto"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:71
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Please verify that you are comparing the correct fingerprint. If "
"fingerprints do not match, %s's account may be compromised and you should "
"consider rejecting this key."
msgstr ""
"Controle ben taconele. Las improntes no coincidin, chel borson di %s al "
"podares no sei lui e tu varesis di mandalu affnacûl lui e la so clâf."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:123
msgid "Verify key fingerprint"
msgstr "Controle la clâf dalas improntes digitâl"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:123
msgid ""
"Compare this key's fingerprint with the fingerprint displayed on the "
"contact's device."
msgstr "Controle las improntes di chiste clâf cun chês tai contas dal tramai."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:125
#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:151
#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:288
msgid "Reject key"
msgstr "Mande affnacûl lui e la clâf"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:125
msgid ""
"Block encrypted communication with the contact's device that uses this key."
msgstr "Smet di cifrà la comunicasion cul pandolo cal dopre chiste clâf."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:127
#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:159
#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:283
msgid "Accept key"
msgstr "Va ben, dami la clâf"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:127
msgid ""
"Allow encrypted communication with the contact's device that uses this key."
msgstr "Permet la comunicasion cifrade cul pandolo cal dopre chiste clâf."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:131
#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:136
#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:140
#, c-format
msgid "This key is currently %s."
msgstr "La clâf a è %s."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:131
msgid "accepted"
msgstr "acetade"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:131
#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:136
#, c-format
msgid "This means it can be used by %s to receive and send encrypted messages."
msgstr "A voul dì ca si po doprà %s par ricevi e mandà mesagjos cifrâs."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:136
msgid "verified"
msgstr "controlade"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:136
msgid ""
"Additionally it has been verified to match the key on the contact's device."
msgstr "In pui si è controlâtche la clâf a sevi che dal contat sul tramai."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:140
msgid "rejected"
msgstr "mandade indavour"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:140
#, c-format
msgid ""
"This means it cannot be used by %s to decipher your messages, and you won't "
"see messages encrypted with it."
msgstr ""
"Al voul dì che %s nola po doprà par decifrà i toi mesagjos, e no tu iodarâs "
"i mesagjos cifrâs cun che lì."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:152
#, c-format
msgid ""
"You won't see encrypted messages from the device of %s that uses this key. "
"Conversely, that device won't be able to decipher your messages anymore."
msgstr ""
"No tu iodarâs i mesagjos cifrâs di %s cal dopre chiste clâf. E lui nol "
"capirà un cai di ce che tu i mandis."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:160
#, c-format
msgid ""
"You will be able to exchange encrypted messages with the device of %s that "
"uses this key."
msgstr ""
"Tu podarâs mandà mesagjos cifrâs cul tramai di %s cal dopre chiste clâf."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/manage_key_dialog.vala:166
msgid "Back"
msgstr "Indavour"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/device_notification_populator.vala:73
msgid "Manage"
msgstr "Gjestis"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/device_notification_populator.vala:80
msgid "This contact has new devices"
msgstr "Chist gnogno al à un gnouf tramai"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/own_notifications.vala:29
msgid "OMEMO trust decision required"
msgstr "Bisugne acetà o no OMEMO"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/own_notifications.vala:31
#, c-format
msgid "Did you add a new device for account %s?"
msgstr "Atu giontât un gnof tramai par il profîl %s?"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:52
msgid "OMEMO by default"
msgstr "OMEMO tal met io"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:53
msgid "Enable OMEMO encryption for new conversations"
msgstr "Permet cifradure OMEMO par las gnoves conversasions"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:54
msgid "Encrypt to new devices"
msgstr "Cifre par i gnoufs tramais"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:55
msgid "Automatically encrypt to new devices from this contact."
msgstr "Cifres su dut par chistu taconele."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:56
msgid "New keys"
msgstr "Gnoves clâs"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:100
msgid ""
"New encryption keys from your other devices will be accepted automatically."
msgstr ""
"Las gnoves clâs par la cifradure di atris tramais a saran acetades cence "
"diti un caj."

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:160
msgid "This device"
msgstr "Chist tramai"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:220
msgid "Other device"
msgstr "Atri tramai"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:220
msgid "Device"
msgstr "Tramai"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:222
msgid "Accepted"
msgstr "acetade"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:225
msgid "Rejected"
msgstr "Mandât affancûl"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:228
msgid "Verified"
msgstr "controlade"

#: plugins/omemo/src/ui/encryption_preferences_entry.vala:277
msgid "New device"
msgstr "Gnouf tramai"

#: plugins/omemo/data/encryption_preferences_entry.ui:8
msgid ""
"Each device has its own OMEMO key. Messages can only be decrypted by a "
"device if they are encrypted to its key. Messages are only encrypted to "
"accepted devices."
msgstr ""
"Ogni tramai al'à la so clâf OMEMO. I mesagjos a podin sei decifrâs nome dal "
"tramai cun che clâf. E nome su tramais acetâs."
